      <hedline>
        <hl1>LAWNSIDE ARENA HALTED</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By ROBERT STRAUSS</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Strauss, Robert</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Mayor Mark Bryant, citing community opposition, decides against building South Jersey Civic Center in Lawnside, NJ (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The new South Jersey Civic Center, an arena planned to put a jolt into the economic development of the small borough of Lawnside, will now not be built there. Mayor Mark Bryant, once a supporter of the arena, withdrew his support last week, citing community opinion against it. County freeholders' second choice for the arena, whose main tenant would be a minor-league hockey team, is in Gloucester Township.</p>
        <p>ROBERT STRAUSS</p>
      </block>
